            </conditions>
            <actions>
                <action id="-9" name="Set value" sid="7411864688069174" type="System">
                    <param id="0" name="Variable">CurrentScript</param>
                    <param id="1" name="Value">NarrativeEndTrigger.StartIndex</param>
                </action>
                <action id="2" name="Set at X" sid="2519635707107466" type="NarrativeArray">
                    <param id="0" name="X">0</param>
                    <param id="1" name="Value">&quot;A plague is spreading through the village. Many have died, and many more will die if we don&apos;t find the cure.&quot;&amp;newline&amp;&quot;(Press the down arrow key to continue)&quot;</param>
                </action>
                <action id="2" name="Set at X" sid="3845996946952913" type="NarrativeArray">
                    <param id="0" name="X">1</param>
                    <param id="1" name="Value">&quot;According to the elders, every time our village has been in peril, the cave has always saved us. They think that the cure to the plague lies in the cave.&quot;</param>
                </action>
                <action id="2" name="Set at X" sid="7371458392058916" type="NarrativeArray">
                    <param id="0" name="X">2</param>
                    <param id="1" name="Value">&quot;As a result, lots of young explorers like me have entered the cave. I&apos;m not part of the Promising Young Explorers&apos; Program, but I think I still have a shot!&quot;</param>
                </action>
                <action id="2" name="Set at X" sid="1928428700503697" type="NarrativeArray">
                    <param id="0" name="X">3</param>
                    <param id="1" name="Value">&quot;&quot;&quot;You... you found the cure?&quot;&quot;&quot;</param>
                </action>
                <action id="2" name="Set at X" sid="4824436850796483" type="NarrativeArray">
                    <param id="0" name="X">4</param>
                    <param id="1" name="Value">&quot;&quot;&quot;Are you sure one of the fine young men from V&apos;s group didn&apos;t help you?&quot;&quot;&quot;</param>
                </action>
                <action id="2" name="Set at X" sid="8315375821111903" type="NarrativeArray">
                    <param id="0" name="X">5</param>
                    <param id="1" name="Value">&quot;&quot;&quot;... yes, Father, I had the help of some of the cave guides, but certainly not any of the other explorers. I can handle myself. And it looks like the villagers treated with the thorn poultice are recovering. So.&quot;&quot;&quot; &amp; newline &amp; &quot;And then I looked at Father H expectantly. Maybe too expectantly. Perhaps it was not proper, but then again, I regret nothing I did that day.&quot;</param>
                </action>
                <action id="2" name="Set at X" sid="3124819922140743" type="NarrativeArray">
                    <param id="0" name="X">6</param>
                    <param id="1" name="Value">&quot;&quot;&quot;... in that case, I suppose we must thank you for your most timely contribution to the village. ... thank you, M.&quot;&quot;&quot;</param>
                </action>
                <action id="2" name="Set at X" sid="8879046259163458" type="NarrativeArray">
                    <param id="0" name="X">7</param>
                    <param id="1" name="Value">&quot;And that was all I got. That was all I got ten years ago.&quot;</param>
                </action>
                <action id="2" name="Set at X" sid="2328805531828612" type="NarrativeArray">
                    <param id="0" name="X">8</param>
                    <param id="1" name="Value">&quot;But now, with the toxic bramble cleared out of the cave, a thorough investigation of the strange inscriptions completed and future pathways built taking them into account...&quot;</param>
                </action>
                <action id="2" name="Set at X" sid="9060753439979574" type="NarrativeArray">
                    <param id="0" name="X">9</param>
                    <param id="1" name="Value">&quot;Eventually, the Fathers let up. The Promising Explorers&apos; Program was modified to include others, too. More girls have joined the program since then.&quot;</param>
                </action>
                <action id="2" name="Set at X" sid="4225159859732157" type="NarrativeArray">
                    <param id="0" name="X">10</param>
                    <param id="1" name="Value">&quot;But really, it should&apos;ve been common sense from the first place, no? I&apos;m just glad it was all sorted out in the end.&quot;</param>
                </action>
                <action id="2" name="Set at X" sid="3243682648600314" type="NarrativeArray">
                    <param id="0" name="X">11</param>
                    <param id="1" name="Value">&quot;Even if I didn&apos;t receive much fanfare from the Fathers at the time, I like to think that my real reward is watching others follow in my footsteps.&quot; &amp;newline&amp; &quot;That&apos;s why I&apos;m becoming a cave guide this year. To provide others the support I didn&apos;t have.&quot;</param>
                </action>
                <action id="2" name="Set at X" sid="7416573939790566" type="NarrativeArray">
                    <param id="0" name="X">12</param>
                    <param id="1" name="Value">&quot;But I&apos;ve said enough about myself now. Storytime&apos;s over! Back to work. Say, isn&apos;t it time for you to lead another exploration?&quot;</param>
                </action>
                <action id="2" name="Set at X" sid="9996510521035968" type="NarrativeArray">
                    <param id="0" name="X">13</param>
                    <param id="1" name="Value">&quot;Designer Credits:&quot; &amp;newline&amp; &quot;Programming: Matt Mistele, Edward Wang, Justin Krasner-Karpen&quot; &amp;newline&amp; &quot;Art: Jessica Kung with special thanks to &apos;My Little Pony&apos;&quot;</param>
                </action>
                <action id="2" name="Set at X" sid="9142546069679263" type="NarrativeArray">
                    <param id="0" name="X">14</param>
                    <param id="1" name="Value">&quot;A special thank you to Mathias Crawford, Dan Klein, and Michael St. Clair, the Grand Dukes of Game Design...&quot;</param>
                </action>
                <action id="2" name="Set at X" sid="1713165624994138" type="NarrativeArray">
                    <param id="0" name="X">15</param>
                    <param id="1" name="Value">&quot;And of course, to you, the player. We bestow upon you the most heartfelt of congratulations. Best of luck to you on your future explorations!&quot;</param>
                </action>
                <action id="0" name="Set text" sid="1642606338525342" type="ScriptText">
